's%20hemp%20crackdown%20should%20be%20a%20wake-up%20call%20for%20the%20industry.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224141%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cann%20beverages.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6917cecbe1a9cbb014de4b13%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224141%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETHC%20drinks%20like%20Cann%20could%20be%20banned%20under%20new%20hemp%20restrictions%20passed%20by%20Congress.%3Cp%3ECann%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECongress%20passed%20hemp%20restrictions%20this%20week%20that%20could%20ban%20THC%20drinks%2C%20a%20billion-dollar%20industry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJake%20Bullock%2C%20CEO%20of%20Cann%2C%20said%20it%20should%20be%20a%20wake-up%20call%20for%20the%20hemp%20industry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBullock%20said%20a%20beverage%20bill%20that%20addresses%20THC%20drinks%20is%20needed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20as-told-to%20essay%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Jake%20Bullock%2C%20the%20cofounder%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-cannabis-beverage-company-cann-fundraising-success-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECEO%20of%20Cann%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%20THC-infused%20beverage%20company.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20funding%20bill%20to%20reopen%20the%20government%2C%20Congress%20passed%20restrictions%20on%20hemp%2C%20set%20to%20take%20effect%20in%20November%202026%2C%20that%20would%20effectively%20ban%20many%20hemp-derived%20THC%20products%2C%20like%20Cann.%20It%20bans%20products%20that%20contain%20more%20than%200.4%20milligrams%20of%20THC%20per%20container.%20This%20story%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20view%20this%20as%20a%20ban.%20It's%20a%20one-year%20shot%20clock%20for%20us%20to%20go%20get%20the%20rules%20that%20we've%20always%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawmakers%20were%20trying%20to%20address%20highly%20potent%20synthetic%20products%2C%20like%20gummy%20candies%2C%20marketed%20toward%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20effort%2C%20led%20by%20Sen.%20Mitch%20McConnell%2C%20was%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20those%20products.%20No%20one's%20talking%20about%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcannabis-thc-drinks-marijuana-laws-regulations-hemp-alcohol-beer-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETHC%20drinks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20far%20less%20potent%20in%20comparison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20that%20reason%2C%20I%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20didn't%20even%20realize%20this%20could%20happen.%20Definitely%20not%20our%20consumers%20who%20love%20these%20products%20and%20not%20even%20our%20alcohol%20partners%2C%20retailers%2C%20and%20distributors%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20have%20reached%20out%20in%20support%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20a%20must-pass%20bill%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fend-of-government-shutdown-what-it-means-airports-snap-aca-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereopen%20the%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20longest%20shutdown%20in%20history%20to%20put%20this%20language%20in.%20It%20would%20not%20have%20happened%20on%20a%20standalone%20basis.%20It%20was%20a%20maneuver%20to%20sneak%20this%20through%20and%20force%20lawmakers'%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20this%20bill%20is%20ultimately%20proposing%2C%20if%20nothing%20gets%20done%20in%20a%20year%2C%20is%20to%20treat%20any%20hemp%20product%20over%200.4%20milligrams%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flegal-marijuana-states-2018-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETHC%20like%20a%20Schedule%20I%3C%2Fa%3E%20drug.%20That%20would%20be%20a%20disaster%20for%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20need%20now%20is%20a%20smart%20beverage%20bill%20that%20would%20allow%20products%20like%20Cann%20to%20be%20sold%20and%20regulated%20like%20alcohol.%20We're%20very%20optimistic%20that%20it%20can%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224912%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jake%20Bullock%20headshot.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6917cdc889026fbb4d0dbc49%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226140%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJake%20Bullock%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Cann%2C%20said%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20new%20legislation%20to%20address%20THC%20drinks.%3Cp%3ECann%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b15837ca-b724-448e-890a-9ed1ea25acbb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EConsumers%2C%20especially%20Gen%20Z%2C%20are%20drinking%20less%20alcohol%20and%20love%20THC%20drinks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETHC%20drinks%20are%20a%20new%20form%20of%20adult%20beverage%2C%20so%20let's%20treat%20them%20like%20adult%20beverages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20certain%20places%20they're%20allowed%20to%20be%20sold%3B%20the%20more%20potent%20they%20are%2C%20the%20more%20controlled%20that%20environment%20is.%20There%20are%20concepts%20for%20serving%20size%20and%20standard%20drinks.%20Alcohol%20is%20taxed%20at%20the%20federal%20level%20through%20the%20Tax%20and%20Trade%20Bureau.%20Consumers%20already%20expect%20THC%20drinks%20to%20be%20sold%20alongside%20alcohol.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-sober-non-alcoholic-economy-restaurants-events-boom-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGen%20Z%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20drinking%20alcohol%20like%20generations%20before.%20Many%20choose%20products%20like%20ours%20because%20they%20don't%20like%20the%20way%20alcohol%20makes%20them%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20love%20that%20consumers%20have%20for%20these%20products%20drives%20my%20optimism.%20A%20couple%20weeks%20ago%2C%20we%20launched%20a%20campaign%20to%20engage%20consumers%20called%20%26quot%3BDon't%20Ban%20Cann.%26quot%3B%20In%2024%20hours%2C%20we%20got%20over%201%2C600%20responses%20with%20people%20telling%20us%20why%20they%20love%20these%20products%2C%20saying%20things%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BCann%20makes%20me%20a%20better%20parent%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BCann%20saved%20my%20marriage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20these%20consumers%20are%20waking%20up%20today%2C%20realizing%20that%20these%20products%20may%20go%20away%2C%20and%20I%20think%20activating%20them%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20key%20part%20of%20our%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225708c18e-91aa-4dcb-bb32-335f978bdc37%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20more%20status%20quo%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20hemp%20restrictions%20were%20well-intentioned%20about%20solving%20a%20very%20specific%20problem%20%E2%80%94%20highly%20potent%20synthetic%20candies.%20We're%20supportive%20of%20solving%20that%20problem%20as%20well.%20But%20don't%20throw%20the%20baby%20out%20with%20the%20bathwater.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20protections%20and%20rules%20for%20these%20drinks%2C%20which%20are%20safe%20and%20very%20low%20in%20strength%2C%20and%20those%20rules%20probably%20should%20be%20similar%20to%20alcohol%20rules%20because%20they%20look%20and%20feel%20a%20lot%20like%20alcohol.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20in%20the%20industry%20made%20the%20mistake%20of%20not%20wanting%20any%20legislation%20with%20restrictive%20language%20around%20hemp.%20Over%20the%20past%20couple%20years%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20messaging%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffarm-bill-legalizes-hemp-boom-marijuana-cbd-industry-2018-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehemp%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bpreserve%20the%20status%20quo.%26quot%3B%20That%20needs%20to%20end.%20Everyone%20should%20be%20waking%20up%20this%20week%20and%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20more%20status%20quo.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20need%20to%20do%20instead%20is%20recognize%20that%20there%20are%20certain%20products%20that%20got%20us%20into%20this%20mess%20that%20should%20not%20be%20allowed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESen.%20Mitch%20McConnell's%20office%20did%20not