20manage%20it%2C%20but%20I%20can%20let%20things%20spin%20me%20up%20pretty%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221bd90f75-f8c8-41b1-8a90-b06a308eacc5%5C%22%3EI%20stack%20my%20habits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20tea%20routine%20includes%20not%20just%20the%20tea%2C%20but%20my%20supplements.%20I%20take%20Vital%20Earth%20Minerals%20Super%20Multi%2C%20a%20liquid%20multivitamin%20with%20fulvic%20minerals.%20I%20keep%20it%20right%20next%20to%20the%20milk%20I%20put%20in%20my%20tea.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-entrepreneur-uses-stoke-stage-stack-framework-run-365-days-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20find%20that%20by%20stacking%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20don't%20forget%20to%20take%20my%20vitamins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20try%20to%20go%20outside.%20It%20makes%20a%20huge%20difference%20in%20helping%20me%20gain%20perspective%20on%20whatever%20issues%20I%20have.%20The%20magnitude%20of%20nature%20helps%20me%20see%20that%20I'm%20putting%20energy%20into%20something%20that%20actually%20doesn't%20matter%20that%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222cd22ed5-8da4-42c5-aaa6-2204a096281c%5C%22%3EI%20get%20on%20a%20yoga%20mat%20almost%20every%20day%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20get%20on%20my%20yoga%20mat%2C%20I%20often%20scan%20my%20email%20for%2030%20to%2045%20minutes.%20I%20generally%20have%20something%20that%20I%20know%20has%20to%20get%20done%2C%20and%20I%20try%20to%20do%20that%20first%20thing%20so%20it's%20not%20hanging%20over%20my%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20get%20to%20my%20yoga%20practice.%20I%20have%20a%20yoga%20teacher%2C%20who%20I've%20been%20working%20with%20for%2015%20years.%20So%2C%20I'll%20either%20get%20on%20my%20mat%20at%20home%20and%20practice%20with%20her%2C%20or%20I'll%20go%20to%20a%20CorePower%20studio%20or%20tune%20in%20to%20a%20livestream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228110%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Niki%20Leondakis%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69163ec